All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComfortCalculator
    Utility class for calculating comfort values.
    DeathEvent
    Represents a death event for an individual.
    Edge
    Represents an edge between two adjacent points on the grid.
    Event
    Abstract class representing an event in the simulation.
    Grid
    Represents the grid with obstacles and special cost zones.
    Grid.SpecialCostZone
    Represents a special cost zone as a rectangle with a cost.
    GridVisualizer
    Provides functionality to visualize the grid and path in ASCII format.
    Individual
    Represents an individual in the simulation with a path and comfort value.
    InputParser
    Handles parsing input from command line arguments or files.
    Main
    The main class for the Pathfinder simulation.
    MoveEvent
    Represents a move event for an individual.
    OutputGenerator
    Handles generating formatted output for the simulation.
    Path
    Represents a path as a sequence of points.
    PEC
    Pending Event Container (PEC) for managing events in the simulation.
    Point
    Represents a point on the grid with x,y coordinates.
    Population
    Manages a collection of individuals in the simulation.
    RandomGenerator
    Utility class for generating random grid elements.
    ReproductionEvent
    Represents a reproduction event for an individual.
    Simulator
    Main simulation engine for the pathfinder problem.
